{"id": 1086, "genre": 1001, "title": "你经历过哪些日常小型恐慌？", "description": "欢迎大家收看今天的《每日一慌》节目。（题目来自：Anne Emond）", "record_count": 6269, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160704024203WalbGB4cV23OopRw.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2016-07-07T03:00:51Z", "options": [{"id": 95873, "content": "手机电量低！", "image": null, "praise_count": 591, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259532}, {"id": 95885, "content": "又没钱了！", "image": "img/option/option/20160707113224w13SBC8OsuT6HEix.jpg", "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 44}, {"id": 96029, "content": "突然想不起要干什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 643040}, {"id": 95883, "content": "手机在哪里?", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 617431}, {"id": 96010, "content": "没Wi-Fi", "image": null, "praise_count": 19, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 441914}, {"id": 95880, "content": "调了7点半的闹钟醒来时却是九点半", "image": null, "praise_count": 332, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 665180}, {"id": 95892, "content": "没钱了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 24, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 166291}, {"id": 95901, "content": "锁门了吗？真的锁了吗？！", "image": null, "praise_count": 266, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 407163}, {"id": 95918, "content": "（下楼后：咦，我刚刚锁门了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 476715}, {"id": 96002, "content": "总觉得闹铃没订，第二天起不来", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 141723}, {"id": 96031, "content": "午睡的时候做连续的噩梦并且起来的时候全身疼", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670664}, {"id": 95870, "content": "梦见自己起床，然而并没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 400, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670125}, {"id": 95900, "content": "朋友们都在忙碌的工作 赚钱 而我在迷茫中", "image": null, "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 498747}, {"id": 95879, "content": "明天穿什么", "image": null, "praise_count": 230, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 627887}, {"id": 95884, "content": "手机放哪了\n我还有什么事没做\n联系不上家人\n迷路了", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658340}, {"id": 95902, "content": "领导在背后走来走去", "image": null, "praise_count": 56, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670170}, {"id": 96000, "content": "梦见上厕所～", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 641043}, {"id": 96018, "content": "下面请一位同学来上黑板做一下这道题。", "image": null, "praise_count": 49, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670126}, {"id": 96024, "content": "面对周一要上班的事实。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 531196}, {"id": 95904, "content": "出门发现没带耳机。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 111, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 585863}, {"id": 95906, "content": "身上木有现金。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 257145}, {"id": 96004, "content": "我的钥匙哪！", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 548389}, {"id": 96006, "content": "突然发现近处有只蜘蛛?️", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670489}, {"id": 96007, "content": "钱包呢", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 541271}, {"id": 96009, "content": "拉屎发现没厕纸", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670583}, {"id": 96011, "content": "做了东西没保存停电了", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670583}, {"id": 96013, "content": "快三十岁了啥也没有", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670603}, {"id": 96015, "content": "考完试玩的正开心，突然想到马上就是出成绩了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670620}, {"id": 96017, "content": "发现一会功夫己经融不进周围的环境", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670624}, {"id": 96026, "content": "经常找手机……", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670651}, {"id": 96032, "content": "路上遇到喜欢的男生发现好几天没有洗头", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 609428}, {"id": 95874, "content": "梦见自己又要准备高考了", "image": null, "praise_count": 140, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669008}, {"id": 95876, "content": "我刚打卡了吗？", "image": null, "praise_count": 128, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 536954}, {"id": 95893, "content": "被堵在路上，眼看要迟到", "image": null, "praise_count": 172, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 179207}, {"id": 95896, "content": "担心自己失业……", "image": null, "praise_count": 21, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669736}, {"id": 104192, "content": "毕业倒计时", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 700756}, {"id": 96001, "content": "刷着公交实时app的“即将到站”狂奔", "image": null, "praise_count": 23, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 491746}, {"id": 96005, "content": "跟他主动说话又好半天不回", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669870}, {"id": 96261, "content": "做梦梦见明天开学", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 349930}, {"id": 96008, "content": "在大巴上尿急", "image": null, "praise_count": 29, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 670583}, {"id": 158985, "content": "眼镜哪去了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 512710}, {"id": 99338, "content": "今天英语没背", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 681377}, {"id": 96267, "content": "地铁门就在自己眼前关上了。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668189}, {"id": 96012, "content": "开车准备找停车位", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 631644}, {"id": 97036, "content": "做题的时候，老师在后面前面左面右面顶着我看呀看呀看呀看！！", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 674567}, {"id": 100620, "content": "睡觉时一只蚊子在耳朵旁飞 删了自己好几巴掌也没拍死", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688253}, {"id": 96014, "content": "翻包，我手机呢？", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 642170}, {"id": 96016, "content": "害怕突然的疾病或事故带走身边重要的人", "image": null, "praise_count": 15, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 669183}, {"id": 96528, "content": "看完这些答案我心慌得要狗带了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 473520}, {"id": 100625, "content": "做了\"不该做的事\",然后他们突然就不怎么理你了，我会想太多，啊？被发现了么？？？", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 688252}]}